text:
[Verse]
City lights look like gold
Wandering through these streets
Dreams unfold I've been told
In the night breathe the beats

[Verse 2]
Hearts racing never slow
Whispers in the dark glow
Catch a glimpse never know
Mysteries start to show

[Chorus]
Under the stars we fly high
Hands up reaching for the sky
Laugh and dance we won't lie
Under the stars pass us by

[Bridge]
Feel the pulse in the air
Electric nights everywhere
We find love we find care
In this moment nothing compares

[Verse 3]
Moonlight guides with a smile
Sit and talk for a while
Worlds apart yet so close
In the night anything goes

[Chorus]
Under the stars we fly high
Hands up reaching for the sky
Laugh and dance we won't lie
Under the stars pass us by
title: Under the Stars
